data.description: Step into this inviting home featuring fresh interior paint and a beautiful updated kitchen complete with a cozy breakfast nook. The open living room features a fireplace that flows into the dining area. The laundry room is conveniently located on the first floor. Upstairs, you'll find two bedrooms, each accompanied by its own full bathroom for added comfort and privacy. Outside, the spacious fenced backyard on a corner lot offers ample room for relaxation and entertainment, all with NO HOA. Conveniently located near Carolina Place Mall, Atrium Health Pineville, and I485. Make it yours today!
